    <etym xml:lang="ru">Возводится к <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>vraza-</w></mentioned> ср.
            <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>vraja-</w><gloss><q>стадо</q></gloss></mentioned>,
        ‘табун’. Другой вариант этого же слова: <ref type="xr" target="#entry_raz"/> | %iiræz%i
        ‘летняя стоянка пастухов’; %ivraja%i- относится к %i(i)ræz%i, %iærwaz%i, как %ivrata%i- к
            <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærwæd"/>.%n<bibl><author>Benveniste</author><ref
                target="#ref_BSL"/><biblScope>LII 34</biblScope></bibl></etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">It traces back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>vraza-</w></mentioned>
        compare <mentioned xml:lang="sa"
        ><lang/><w>vraja-</w><gloss><q>flock</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘herd’. Another variant of the
        same word is <ref type="xr" target="#entry_raz"/> | %iiræz%i ‘summer station for shepherds’;
        %ivraja%i- relates to %i(i)ræz%i, %iærwaz%i, like %ivrata%i- relates to <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_ærwæd"/>%n<bibl><author>Benveniste</author><ref target="#ref_BSL"
                /><biblScope>LII 34</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
